OL,3,CFamilies feel 'trapped' waiting for
OL,4,Cremoval of unsafe cladding
OL,6,FWatch: ITV News Meridian's report is
OL,7,Fby Charlotte Wilkins
OL,9,FPeople living in blocks of flats in
OL,10,FBrighton say it is essential that
OL,11,Fflammable cladding on their homes is
OL,12,Fmade safe as soon as possible, telling
OL,13,FITV News Meridian they feel 'trapped'.
OL,15,FThe demand from those at the City
OL,16,FPoint development comes after a
OL,17,Fwatchdog says some householders across
OL,18,Fthe country could have to live with
OL,19,Fthe cladding for another ten years and
OL,20,Fmore.
