OL,3,CFamilies feel 'trapped' waiting for
OL,4,Cremoval of unsafe cladding
OL,6,FIn the Budget last week, Chancellor
OL,7,FRachel Reeves pledged that the
OL,8,Fgovernment would "make progress on our
OL,9,Fcommitment to accelerate the
OL,10,Fremediation of homes following the
OL,11,Ffindings of the Grenfell Inquiry, with
OL,12,F#1 billion of investment to remove
OL,13,Fdangerous cladding next year".
OL,15,FAnna Belabbes, a mother living at City
OL,16,FPoint, says she is worried about the
OL,17,Fsafety of her family and neighbours if
OL,18,Fa fire were to break out.
