OL,3,CFamilies feel 'trapped' waiting for
OL,4,Cremoval of unsafe cladding
OL,6,F"It is very worrying. Not only for
OL,7,Fmyself, but my neighbours, my
OL,8,Fchildren. We've had this temporary
OL,9,Ffire escape which looks appalling and
OL,10,Fit looks really unsafe.
OL,12,F"The lights don't work in the corridor
OL,13,Fso, heaven forbid, there ever was a
OL,14,Ffire going on, I really worry about
OL,15,Fthe consequences of being able to
OL,16,Fescape safely."
OL,18,FThe City Point development is covered
OL,19,Fin expanded polystyrene render which
OL,20,Fwas deemed unsafe following fire
OL,21,Fsafety inspections.
