OL,3,CFamilies feel 'trapped' waiting for
OL,4,Cremoval of unsafe cladding
OL,6,FMore than 250 people living there were
OL,7,Finformed that the cladding would not
OL,8,Fbe removed until the summer of 2025.
OL,9,FThere is currently no centralised fire
OL,10,Falarm system in the building.
OL,12,FThe developers, Barratt Redrow, said
OL,13,Fthat contractors for the external
OL,14,Fcladding will be appointed in the
OL,15,Fcoming weeks.
