OL,3,CFamilies feel 'trapped' waiting for
OL,4,Cremoval of unsafe cladding
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "Work at City
OL,7,FPoint is progressing, fire alarms have
OL,8,Fbeen installed in all communal areas
OL,9,Fand over the next six weeks fire
OL,10,Falarms will be added to every
OL,11,Fapartment.
OL,13,F"Over the coming weeks we will be
OL,14,Fappointing a contractor to carry out
OL,15,Fexternal wall surveys to prepare the
OL,16,Fdesign and specification of the
OL,17,Fremedial works for application to the
OL,18,FBuilding Safety Regulator (BSR) ahead
OL,19,Fof the work taking place in summer
OL,20,F2025."
