OL,3,CFamilies feel 'trapped' waiting for
OL,4,Cremoval of unsafe cladding
OL,6,FMeanwhile the management company for
OL,7,FCity Point, First Port, said that the
OL,8,Fprocess to start work has taken
OL,9,F'longer than expected'.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "The remediation
OL,12,Fproject at City Point has commenced,
OL,13,Fwith all investigatory works to
OL,14,Fidentify the scope of the remediation
OL,15,Frequired complete.
OL,17,F"We remain in regular contact with the
OL,18,Fdeveloper, Barratt, to ensure progress
OL,19,Fis made as quickly as possible, whilst
OL,20,Fprioritising the safety of our
OL,21,Fresidents at every stage.
