OL,3,CFamilies feel 'trapped' waiting for
OL,4,Cremoval of unsafe cladding
OL,6,F"This has been a longer process than
OL,7,Fexpected due to the requirement for
OL,8,Fadditional fire safety measures to be
OL,9,Fimplemented. This work is ongoing, and
OL,10,Fwe are continuing to keep residents
OL,11,Fupdated."
OL,13,FBuilding safety minister Alex Norris
OL,14,Fsaid: "The pace of remediation to make
OL,15,Fhomes safe has been unacceptably slow.
OL,17,F"This Government is taking action,
OL,18,Fmeeting our commitment to invest #5.1
OL,19,Fbillion to remove dangerous cladding
OL,20,Fand making sure those responsible pay
OL,21,Ffor the rest.
