OL,6,F"This Government will protect
OL,7,Fleaseholders and empower regulators to
OL,8,Ftake enforcement action against those
OL,9,Fbuilding owners who fail to act.
OL,11,F"Since coming into office, we have
OL,12,Framped up work with local authorities
OL,13,Fand regulators to speed up remediation
OL,14,Fand we will set out a remediation
OL,15,Facceleration plan soon."
